    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルカ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ruca</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>さーてと。
ウゼェのも片付けたし
さっさと行こうぜェ、ルカ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Alrighty then.
We've dealt with those annoyances.
Let's hurry and get outta here, Ruca.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ねぇ、スパーダ。
不思議に思ってたんだけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Say, Spada. I thought it was odd, but...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんでスパーダは
僕と一緒に来てくれる気になったの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why did you decide to come with me?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あぁ？　そんなの決まってんだろ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? Ain't that obvious?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>世界樹に辿り着くなんて無理だよ〜！
って泣き叫ぶルカを
一番近くで見る為だよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I wanted to see ya cryin' out like, "It's not even
possible to reach the World Treeee〜!" from
as close as I possibly could.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そ、そんな理由だったんだ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>S-So that's why...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
